title: 2024 Hong Kong Tennis Open – Singles
content:
Diana Shnaider defeated Katie Boulter in the final, 6–1, 6–2 to win the singles tennis title at the 2024 Hong Kong Tennis Open.[1] It was her fourth WTA Tour title.[2]

Leylah Fernandez was the defending champion,[3] but lost to Shnaider in the semifinals.[4]
